      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-24T18:06:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Put that in your commit message.  Based on my read of that quote, the current code implements that correctly.  You\u0027re trying to change a different case (object doesn\u0027t exist).",
      "parentUuid": "681bf125_6754f9f1",
